Package: com.trackerscan.cli
Name: trackerscan
Version: 0.1.0
Architecture: iphoneos-arm
Description: On-device detector for iOS tracking libraries. Reads
 Objective-C class names from volatile process memory of
 legitimately-installed apps and matches them against a bundled
 signature list. Writes no files and does not decrypt or reproduce
 app binaries.
Depends: firmware (>= 15.0)
Maintainer: hello@trackercontrol.org
Author: hello@trackercontrol.org
Section: Security
